"a SMS message containing a brief explanation and the verification code is sent to ComCompany together with the given phone number."
@postF
"the ctAuthenticated to which the actor is related to is associated with a newly generated 'ctVCode' instance with its \newline
'dtTime' attribute set to the current ctState clock information \newline
'dtVCode' attribute generated randomly \newline
and 'isValidated' attribute set to false
"
@endPostF
//postProtocol descriptions
